## Common Operations

### Health Check

```bash
# Check service health
curl -s http://{{serviceHost}}/health | jq .

# Check specific endpoint
curl -s http://{{serviceHost}}/ready | jq .
```

### Restart Service

```bash
# Kubernetes
kubectl rollout restart deployment/{{serviceName}} -n {{namespace}}

# Docker
docker restart {{serviceName}}
```

### Scale Service

```bash
# Scale to N replicas
kubectl scale deployment/{{serviceName}} --replicas={{replicas}} -n {{namespace}}
```

